Grammar

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: stmt
    2        | program stmt

    3 stmt: expr PUNCTUATION
    4     | KEYWORD PUNCTUATION
    5     | PUNCTUATION

    6 expr: expr op term
    7     | term

    8 op: OPERATOR
    9   | KEYWORD

   10 term: ID
   11     | INTCONST
   12     | REAL
   13     | STRING


