State 0

    0 $accept: • program $end

    KEYWORD      shift, and go to state 1
    INTCONST     shift, and go to state 2
    REAL         shift, and go to state 3
    STRING       shift, and go to state 4
    PUNCTUATION  shift, and go to state 5
    ID           shift, and go to state 6

    program  go to state 7
    stmt     go to state 8
    expr     go to state 9
    term     go to state 10


